{"tid":2100752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（成功爭取）60歲$2乘車優惠   民建聯指羅致光承諾提前今年底推行","createTime":"2020-07-09T09:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:27:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"26f90d45a14b07697664ad84bbab1f4b2942b64f","tid":2100752,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光早前指2港元乘車優惠年齡門檻將由65歲下調至60歲，目標於明年底實施，被炮轟太遲。 有議員今日與羅致光表達不滿後，又引述羅承諾會提早於今年底推行相關政策。<br />\n<br />\n議員鄭泳舜及陳恒鑌表示，今日與羅致光會面，指相關政策至明年底才實施太遲，又引述羅承諾會提早於今年底推行政策。<br />\n<br />\n2名議員提到相關撥款需交由下屆立法，又要經財務委員會審議通過，希望屆時立法會可以盡快批出款項，令長者受惠。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200709/bkn-20200709170957871-0709_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2bddced984ea0d7030a8f7f972a7dbdbff3724f2","tid":2100752,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23563b98a247c1eb60b94b6e8554422b4f845f11","tid":2100752,"uid":215734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bddced984ea0d7030a8f7f972a7dbdbff3724f2","tid":2100752,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"巴士唔係不嬲都60歲咩"},{"pid":"abf22387d6e0c6647b39b3823fb15387136ae23d","tid":2100752,"uid":147367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bddced984ea0d7030a8f7f972a7dbdbff3724f2","tid":2100752,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府補貼架"},{"pid":"d9fdddefcaaf64a40285385c8846f4eab726e62a","tid":2100752,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebecbffa0889239e274773587747ce589